    • Event

      public Event(String id, String name, String location, LocalDateTime startTime, LocalDateTime endTime, String details, ArrayList<Integer> milestones, boolean trackLocation)
      Constructor for all non-photo attributes (photos are initialized via default constructor)
      Parameters:
      id - unique ID number for event
      name - name of event
      location - location of event
      startTime - date and time (year, month, day, hour, minute) of event start
      endTime - date and time (year, month, day, hour, minute) of event end
      details - paragraph of event details
      milestones - list of attendance milestones to track
      trackLocation - is location tracking of check-ins enabled

    • Event

      public Event(String id, String name, String location, LocalDateTime startTime, LocalDateTime endTime, String details, ArrayList<Integer> milestones, QRCode checkInQR, QRCode promoQR, boolean trackLocation, List<String> checkedInAttendees)
      Constructor for all attributes
      Parameters:
      id - unique ID number for event
      name - name of event
      location - location of event
      startTime - date and time (year, month, day, hour, minute) of event start
      endTime - date and time (year, month, day, hour, minute) of event end
      details - paragraph of event details
      milestones - list of attendance milestones to track
      checkInQR - QR code used to check user in to event
      promoQR - QR code used to promote the event
      trackLocation - is location tracking of check-ins enabled
      checkedInAttendees - list of checked in attendees
